ActJudges Act (Removal Allowance) Order
PrecisOrder prescribing an additional period during which certain RELOCATION EXPENSES may be reimbursed to The Hon. RAYMOND P. WHALEN, who was required to relocate to the the City of Gander in the Province of Newfoundland and Labrador following his appointment as a Judge of the Trial Division of the Supreme Court of Newfoundland and Labrador on June 18, 2008.
